Package: text
Type: Package
Title: Analyses of Text using Natural Language Processing and Machine Learning
Version: 0.6.0.9000
Author: Oscar Kjell & Andrew Schwartz
Maintainer: The package maintainer <oscar.kjell@psy.lu.se>
Description: Transforms text variables to word embeddings; where the word embeddings are used to statistically test the mean difference between set of texts, compute semantic similarity scores between texts, predict numerical variables, and visual statisticall significant words according to various dimensions etc.   
